[area=Town Vanilla Cop]Welcome!

You are a [b][color=forestgreen]Town Vanilla Cop[/color][/b].

You may target one player per night phase. At the end of the night phase, you will be informed that they are [color=cream]Vanilla[/color] if they are a vanilla townie or a mafia goon. If they are a power role of either alignment, you will be informed that they are [color=grey]Not Vanilla Townie[/color]. If you are roleblocked, you will receive no result.

[b]You win when all threats to the Town have been eliminated.[/b]

The game thread is [url=PUBLICTHREAD]here[/url].

Confirm by replying with your role name and alignment.[/area]
